[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis of the Issues[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter analyzing the code snippets and the evaluation report, I've identified the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mroot causes of both the timeout and compilation error:[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m. **Primary Issue: Infinite Loop in [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLine [0m[1;36m247[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe do-while loop structure at lines [0m[1;36m120[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m247[0m[39m can enter an infinite loop when the [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbuffer contains only whitespace or NULL bytes. The `skip` flag is set to `true` at [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlines [0m[1;36m199[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m204[0m[39m, causing the outer do-while loop to repeat indefinitely without [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mever returning a token.[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m. **Secondary Issue: Unbounded Search Loops in [0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTwo search loops [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m have no iteration limits and can hang [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif target tokens aren't found. The second loop also has a potential NPE risk when [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalling `[0m[1;35mpeekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` without null checking.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m. **Compilation Error: Duplicate Variable Declaration**[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch incorrectly declared `searchIterations` twice in the same method scope [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m560[0m[39m and [0m[1;36m650[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, violating Java's scoping rules.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m. **Additional Risk: Third Unbounded Loop in [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mLines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m also contain an unbounded search loop with NPE risk.[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Part A: Fix Type1Lexer.java - Consecutive Skip Counter[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.java`[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Add constant** after line [0m[1;36m51[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter the LOG declaration[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final int MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m;[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This value allows legitimate fonts with many whitespace characters while [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpreventing infinite loops[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Follows the pattern from BaseParser.java with MAX_LENGTH_LONG constant[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Initialize counter** at line [0m[1;36m119[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39minside [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method, before the [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mdo-while loop[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int consecutiveSkips = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Increment and check after line [0m[1;36m199[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwhitespace handling[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   else if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mCharacter.isWhitespace[0m[1;39m([0m[39mc[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       skip = true;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       consecutiveSkips++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconsecutiveSkips > MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[32m"Excessive consecutive whitespace or NULL bytes at position "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mbuffer.position[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m", possible infinite loop"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Increment and check after line [0m[1;36m204[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mNULL byte handling[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   else if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mc == [0m[1;36m0[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mLOG.warn[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"NULL byte in font, skipped"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       skip = true;[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       consecutiveSkips++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mconsecutiveSkips > MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[32m"Excessive consecutive whitespace or NULL bytes at position "[0m[39m + [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[1;35mbuffer.position[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m + [0m[32m", possible infinite loop"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: This approach tracks consecutive skip operations across do-while [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miterations. Once a non-skip character is encountered, the method returns a token [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand the counter is naturally reset for the next invocation. This preserves the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexisting token reading logic while preventing infinite loops.[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Part B: Fix Type1Parser.java - Search Loop Iteration Limits[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java`[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Add constant** after line [0m[1;36m45[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mafter CHARSTRING_KEY[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m maximum iterations for unbounded search loops[0m                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   private static final int MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m;[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This allows searching through large font dictionaries while preventing [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeouts[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Follows the established pattern for MAX constants in the codebase[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **In [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method**, declare counter variable once at line [0m[1;36m554[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mright [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mafter `lexer = new [0m[1;35mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m([0m[39mdecrypted[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   int searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Modify first search loop** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m556[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to include iteration check:[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   Token peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   while [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken != null && ![0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpeekToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m for a more thorough validation, the presence of [0m[32m"begin"[0m[39m before Private[0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m determines how code before and following charstrings should look[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m it is not currently checked anyway[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       searchIterations++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[32m"Could not find /Private dictionary within iteration limit, possible[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mmalformed font"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Reset counter before second search loop** at line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m:[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Reset counter for CharStrings search[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m some fonts have [0m[32m"2 index"[0m[39m here, others have [0m[32m"end noaccess put"[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m sometimes followed by [0m[32m"put"[0m[39m. Either way, we just skip until[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m the [0m[35m/[0m[95mCharStrings[0m[39m dict is found[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   while [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Modify second search loop body** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m642[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with null check and iteration[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlimit:[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```java[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Check for unexpected end of tokens[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Unexpected end of file while searching for [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32m/CharStrings dictionary"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       searchIterations++;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m           throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m               [0m[32m"Could not find /CharStrings dictionary within iteration limit, [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mpossible malformed font"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m       [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   ```[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Fix [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m with similar protection:[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add local counter: `int encodingSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;`[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Add null check inside loop[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Increment and check counter[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - This ensures consistency across all search loops[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: By declaring `searchIterations` once at method level and resetting [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mit between search phases, we avoid the duplicate variable error while maintaining [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mseparate iteration limits for each search operation. The null checks prevent NPEs [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand provide clearer error messages. Reusing the same counter variable is idiomatic [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mJava and reduces memory overhead.[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Why This Is the Optimal Approach[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: The fix doesn't change the core tokenization or [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparsing algorithms, only adds safety guards against infinite loops.[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Follows Codebase Patterns**: [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses MAX constants like BaseParser.java[0m                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throws DamagedFontException like existing Type1Lexer code[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Checks for null tokens like [0m[1;35mreadProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, [0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, and [0m[1;35mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Comprehensive Coverage**: Fixes all three unbounded loops [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtwo in [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, one in [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and the lexer skip loop.[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Proper Error Handling**: Throws appropriate exceptions with descriptive [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmessages including context [0m[1;39m([0m[39mposition, dictionary name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **No Breaking Changes**: [0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate fonts will parse normally [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlimits are generous[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only malformed/malicious fonts trigger the new exceptions[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - All existing tests should pass[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **Compilation Safety**: Resolves the duplicate variable error by declaring once [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand reusing.[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Potential Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Legitimate fonts with excessive whitespace**: Mitigated by setting [0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mMAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS high enough [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Large complex fonts**: Mitigated by setting MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS high enough [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m([0m[1;36m100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m.[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Changed error messages**: Now throws DamagedFontException instead of timeout, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich is actually better for debugging.[0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Performance**: Minimal impact - just integer increments and comparisons in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops that were already executing.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mBaseParser.readStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m uses MAX_LENGTH_LONG to limit number parsing[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readRegular[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m has position-based loop protection[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;35mType1Parser.readProc[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m and [0m[1;35mreadSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m check for null tokens inside loops[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis fix applies these established patterns consistently across the vulnerable code[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpaths.[0m                                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m894[0m[39m:            throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Found "[0m[39m + token + [0m[32m" but expected "[0m[39m + name[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m895[0m[39m:        [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
