[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mcode_snippets[0m[39m>[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Fix Strategy[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<fix_strategy>[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Analysis[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter reviewing the evaluation report and code snippets, I've identified the root [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcause of the persistent timeout issue:[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Problem Identification[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Initial Issue**: Timeout in `[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m247[0m[39m due to [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexcessive whitespace/NULL byte processing[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Patch Applied**: Added `MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS` limit to Type1Lexer and [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration limits to some loops in Type1Parser[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Post-Patch Issue**: Timeout moved to `[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m, [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mindicating the patch was incomplete[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Root Cause[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe code has **three unbounded search loops** in Type1Parser that lack proper [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msafeguards:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Line [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"dup"[0m[39m, [0m[32m"readonly"[0m[39m, or [0m[32m"def"[0m[39m tokens[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- NO null check, NO iteration limit[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Line [0m[1;36m557[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseBinary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"Private"[0m[39m token - HAS null check [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbut NO iteration limit  [0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mparseBinary[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Searches for [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m token - NO null [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcheck, NO iteration limit ⭐ **Current timeout location**[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch apparently added protection to loop #[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m but **completely missed loop #[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m**,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhich is where the timeout now occurs. Loop #[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m also remains vulnerable.[0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Causes Timeouts[0m                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mWhen a malicious fuzzer crafts segment2 data with:[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Millions of valid tokens that don't include [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Or intermixed whitespace that resets the Type1Lexer skip counter[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe loop at line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m will iterate millions of times, each calling:[0m                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - returns non-null token[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- `[0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` - advances to next token[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Repeating until timeout [0m[1;39m([0m[39m~[0m[1;36m28[0m[39m seconds CPU time[0m[1;39m)[0m                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Comprehensive Fix Strategy[0m                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m1[0m[39m: Add Iteration Limit Constant to Type1Parser[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAdd after the existing encryption constants [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m45[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [35m/[0m[35m/[0m[39m Maximum iterations for unbounded search loops to prevent timeout on malformed [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfonts[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mprivate static final int MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m;[0m                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Rationale**: [0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Normal Type1 fonts have hundreds to thousands of tokens[0m                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- [0m[1;36m100[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m provides 10[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m safety margin for legitimate fonts[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Matches the codebase pattern [0m[1;39m([0m[39me.g., PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH = 100MB[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Will execute in milliseconds, well under timeout threshold[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m: Fix Loop #[0m[1;36m1[0m[39m - [0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m223[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: In the `[0m[1;35mreadEncoding[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, before the while loop at line [0m[1;36m217[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Add iteration counter before the loop[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add null check inside the loop before calling `[0m[1;35mgetText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Add iteration limit check with DamagedFontException[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Increment counter after each iteration[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Pattern**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.NAME[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"dup"[0m[1;39m)[0m                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"readonly"[0m[1;39m)[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m                || [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"def"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Token token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"Expected dup, readonly or def token not found in [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mencoding"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    searchIterations++;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m searching for encoding entry markers"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m3[0m[39m: Fix Loop #[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m - [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m Private Search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m557[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m564[0m[1;39m)[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: In the `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, before the while loop at line [0m[1;36m557[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Add iteration counter before the loop[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add iteration limit check with DamagedFontException [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnull check already exists[0m[1;39m)[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Increment counter after each iteration[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Pattern**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint searchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mToken peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken != null && ![0m[32m"Private"[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mpeekToken.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    searchIterations++;[0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39msearchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m searching for /Private token"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    peekToken = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mif [0m[1;39m([0m[39mpeekToken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/Private token not found"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m: Fix Loop #[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m - [0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m CharStrings Search [0m[1;39m([0m[39mLines [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m644[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m ⭐ [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**CRITICAL**[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Location**: In the `[0m[1;35mparseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method, before the while loop at line [0m[1;36m640[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Changes**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Add iteration counter before the loop[0m                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Add null check inside the loop before calling `[0m[1;35mgetText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Add iteration limit check with DamagedFontException[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Increment counter after each iteration[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. Add null check exception after the loop[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Pattern**:[0m                                                                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```java[0m                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mint charStringsSearchIterations = [0m[1;36m0[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhile [0m[1;39m([0m[39m![0m[1;39m([0m[1;35mlexer.peekKind[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken.LITERAL[0m[1;39m)[0m                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        && [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.getText[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[1;35m.equals[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m[1;39m)[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m{[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    Token token = [0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mtoken == null[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mIOException[0m[1;39m([0m[32m"/CharStrings token not found in Private [0m             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mdictionary"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;35mlexer.nextToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    charStringsSearchIterations++;[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    if [0m[1;39m([0m[39mcharStringsSearchIterations > MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS[0m[1;39m)[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m{[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m        throw new [0m[1;35mDamagedFontException[0m[1;39m([0m                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"Exceeded maximum iterations [0m[32m([0m[32m"[0m[39m + MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS + [0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m            [0m[32m"[0m[32m)[0m[32m searching for /CharStrings token"[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m;[0m                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m    [0m[1;39m}[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;39m}[0m                                                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m```[0m                                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Note**: Use a different variable name [0m[1;39m([0m[39m`charStringsSearchIterations`[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to avoid [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconflict with the earlier `searchIterations` variable in the same method.[0m           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Step [0m[1;36m5[0m[39m: Reapply Previous Type1Lexer Patches [0m[1;39m([0m[39mIf Not Already Present[0m[1;39m)[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mBased on the evaluation report, the previous patch to Type1Lexer should be [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mmaintained:[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS constant**: Keep the limit of [0m[1;36m10[0m[39m,[0m[1;36m000[0m[39m consecutive [0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwhitespace/NULL skips[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **consecutiveSkips counter in [0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Keep the counter and checks[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **DamagedFontException on limit**: Keep the exception throwing[0m                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThese changes prevent the lexer itself from getting stuck in skip loops.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Justification[0m                                                                    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Why This Is the Optimal Approach[0m                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Addresses Root Cause**: Directly fixes all three unbounded search loops that [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcan cause timeouts[0m                                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Follows Codebase Patterns**: [0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses DamagedFontException like existing code [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m164[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m165[0m[39m, [0m[1;36m223[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m224[0m[39m in [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mType1Lexer[0m[1;39m)[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Uses MAX_* constants like PfbParser.MAX_LENGTH and BaseParser.MAX_LENGTH_LONG[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Follows the defensive null-check pattern from loop #[0m[1;36m2[0m[39m [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m565[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m568[0m[1;39m)[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Preserves Existing Logic**: [0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Doesn't change the parsing algorithm or token recognition[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Maintains the same token search behavior[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only adds safety limits to prevent abuse[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Minimal Impact**: [0m                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Legitimate fonts process normally [0m[1;39m([0m[39mwell under 100K iterations[0m[1;39m)[0m                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Only malformed/malicious fonts trigger the exceptions[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - No performance impact on normal operations[0m                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### How It Addresses the Evaluation Report Issues[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Initial Issue [0m[1;39m([0m[39mreadToken timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Already addressed by previous Type1Lexer [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mpatch[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Post-Patch Issue [0m[1;39m([0m[39mline [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m timeout[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: **Directly fixed** by Step [0m[1;36m4[0m[39m adding [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39miteration limit to CharStrings search[0m                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Prevents Future Issues**: Steps [0m[1;36m2[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m3[0m[39m protect the other vulnerable loops[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Side Effects and Mitigation[0m                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Potential Side Effects**:[0m                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Extremely unusual fonts with >100K tokens before [0m[32m"CharStrings"[0m[39m would be rejected[0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- This is acceptable as such fonts are either malformed or malicious[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**Mitigation**:[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Use DamagedFontException [0m[1;39m([0m[39mnot generic IOException[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m to clearly indicate font [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcorruption[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- Provide descriptive error messages showing which token was being searched[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- The 100K limit is 10[0m[1;36m0x[0m[39m larger than typical fonts, minimizing false positives[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Similar Solutions in Codebase[0m                                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThis approach mirrors existing protections:[0m                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mPfbParser.parsePfb[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m162[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m164[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Checks size limits and throws [0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mIOException[0m                                                                         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mBaseParser.readStringNumber[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m** [0m[1;39m([0m[39mlines [0m[1;36m1450[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m1454[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m: Limits number length and [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthrows IOException  [0m                                                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m- **[0m[1;35mType1Parser.readSubrs[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[35m/[0m[95mreadCharStrings[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m**: Use bounded for-loops with early [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mexits[0m                                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Expected Outcome[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying this fix:[0m                                                            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The timeout at line [0m[1;36m640[0m[39m will be eliminated[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. All three unbounded search loops will have iteration limits[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Fuzzer will trigger DamagedFontException instead of timeout[0m                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. Legitimate Type1 fonts will continue to parse correctly[0m                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. The fix will be complete and robust against similar timeout attacks[0m              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m<[0m[35m/[0m[95mfix_strategy[0m[1m>[0m                                                                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         ===Evaluation [33mEnd[0m===                                                                [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Summary[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue reports a libFuzzer timeout occurring during PDF text extraction [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations. The main thread is stuck in a runnable state within the [0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m`[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method at line [0m[1;36m247[0m[39m, specifically in a native trace [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mand unbounded token searches. However, applying the patch did not resolve the [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mtimeout issue, as the same error persists.[0m                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m## Description[0m                                                                      [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Initial Issue Analysis[0m                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe initial issue presents a timeout error during fuzzing of PDF text extraction [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mfunctionality. Key observations from the thread dump include:[0m                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **Primary Thread State**: The main thread [0m[1;39m([0m[39m#[0m[1;36m1[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m is in RUNNABLE state and has [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mconsumed significant CPU time [0m[1;39m([0m[1;36m26660.[0m[39m43ms out of [0m[1;36m28.[0m[39m61s elapsed[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m, indicating a [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomputational loop rather than a blocking operation.[0m                                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **Call Stack**: The execution path shows:[0m                                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Specific location: `[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` at line [0m[1;36m247[0m                        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **Font Processing Context**: The timeout occurs during Type1 font creation from [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39mwithin the binary parsing phase of Type1 font parsing.[0m                              [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Patch Attempt Details[0m                                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mThe patch introduces safeguards in two files:[0m                                       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Lexer.java`**[0m          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Added a constant `MAX_CONSECUTIVE_SKIPS = [0m[1;36m10000[0m[39m` to limit consecutive skip [0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39moperations[0m                                                                          [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modified the `[0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[39mToken prevToken[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` method to:[0m                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Introduce a counter `consecutiveSkips` initialized to [0m[1;36m0[0m                        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Increment the counter when whitespace characters are encountered [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Throw `DamagedFontException` when consecutive skips exceed the maximum [0m        [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m**File: `fontbox/src/main/java/org/apache/fontbox/type1/Type1Parser.java`**[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. Added a constant `MAX_SEARCH_ITERATIONS = [0m[1;36m100000[0m[39m` for loop iteration limits[0m      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. Modified encoding parsing logic [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m217[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m235[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m                           [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Added null check for `[0m[1;35mlexer.peekToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m`[0m                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. Modified binary parsing in the private dictionary search [0m[1;39m([0m[39maround line [0m[1;36m567[0m[39m-[0m[1;36m585[0m[1;39m)[0m[39m:[0m  [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m         [39m   - Increments counter on each token advance[0m                                       [2m                [0m

[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Post-Patch Result[0m                                                               [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mAfter applying the patch, the timeout error persists with the same [0m[32m"ERROR: [0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [32mlibFuzzer: timeout"[0m[39m message. This indicates that:[0m                                   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. The introduced limits were either not reached during execution, suggesting the [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minfinite loop occurs elsewhere[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. The limits may not be applied to the actual problematic code path[0m                [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. The timeout occurs in a different execution context not covered by the patch[0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39m### Areas Requiring Further Investigation[0m                                           [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mTo obtain a comprehensive understanding of the timeout issue, the following areas [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mshould be examined:[0m                                                                 [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m1[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Lexer.readToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method**: The complete implementation at line [0m[1;36m247[0m[39m and [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39msurrounding code, particularly any loops or conditional logic that might not have [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mbeen covered by the patch. The stack trace specifically points to this line, but [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mthe patch modifications may not address the exact problematic code segment.[0m         [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m2[0m[39m. **[0m[1;35mType1Parser.parseBinary[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m method**: At line [0m[1;36m643[0m[39m in the call stack, this method[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcalls into the lexer. The complete implementation should be reviewed for unbounded [0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops or recursive patterns not addressed by the current patch.[0m                     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m3[0m[39m. **ByteBuffer reading operations**: Since the lexer operates on a ByteBuffer, [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39minvestigate whether the buffer manipulation itself could cause infinite iterations,[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparticularly in malformed font data scenarios.[0m                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m4[0m[39m. **Character comparison logic**: The native method `traceConstCmpInt` in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mstack suggests integer comparisons are being traced. Examine the character/byte [0m    [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomparison logic in `[0m[1;35mreadToken[0m[1;39m([0m[1;39m)[0m[39m` that might be evaluated repeatedly without [0m       [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvancing the buffer position.[0m                                                      [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m5[0m[39m. **Token parsing state machine**: Review the overall state management in the [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mlexer to identify if certain input patterns could cause the parser to remain in a [0m  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mparticular state indefinitely without triggering the newly added safeguards.[0m        [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m6[0m[39m. **The `skip` flag logic**: The patch adds counters for when `[0m[33mskip[0m[39m=[0m[35mtrue[0m[39m`, but the[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mcomplete do-while loop structure and all conditions that set or reset the `skip` [0m   [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mflag need examination to ensure all infinite loop scenarios are covered.[0m            [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [1;36m7[0m[39m. **Buffer position advancement**: Verify that all code paths within the loop [0m     [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39madvance the buffer position appropriately, as failure to do so would cause infinite[0m [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m         [39mloops regardless of skip counting.[0m                                                  [2m                [0m
[2;36m                    [0m                                                                                             [2m                [0m
